import React from 'react' import { Grid, Typography } from '@material-ui/core' import { resume_data } from '../../utils/resumeData'; import CustomTimeline, { CustomTimelineSeparator } from '../../components/Timeline/Timeline'; import TimelineDot from '@mui/lab/TimelineDot'; import WorkIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Work'; import SchoolIcon from '@mui/icons-material/School'; import TerminalIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Terminal'; import './Resume.css' import { TimelineItem } from '@material-ui/lab'; import { TimelineContent } from '@mui/lab'; import { Paper, typographyClasses } from '@mui/material'; export const CustomTitle = ({title}) => { return ( <>
{title}
) } const Resume = () => { return ( <> {/* About Me */} {resume_data.about} {/* Resume */} } title={'Work History'}> {resume_data.experiences.map((experience) =>( {experience.title} {experience.company} - {experience.years} {experience.description} ))} } title={'Education history'}> {resume_data.education.map((education) =>( {education.title} {education.years} {education.description} ))} } title={'Projects'}> {resume_data.hackathons.map((hackathons) =>( {hackathons.title} {hackathons.event} {hackathons.description} ))} {/* Services */} {resume_data.services.map(service => (
{service.icon} {service.title} {service.description}
))} {/*Skills*/} {resume_data.skills.map(skill => ( {skill.title} {skill.description.map(elm =>( {elm} ))} ))} ) } export default Resume
